Quote:  Karen McNulty is a post board operator. ... Post board operator still doesn't rank high as a preferred occupation though the colloquial term `chalkie' is now better known than it was BC (before crash). Chalkies were on television a lot last October - ... flitting from blackboard to blackboard, armed with chalk and duster, squiggling the hieroglyphs that rule the world via the stock exchange.
